Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走着去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那有着各种各样的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既温暖又快乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 妈妈 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和早苗阿姨是怎么玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有带书来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.65,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹田德广：日本著名棒球运动员，拥有满垒男的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔到底教了些什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈你听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 妈妈 妈妈听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吵吵闹闹地多羞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为妈妈你不听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考虑一下周围的人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 想上厕所的话先说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说不可以哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 那个人竟会这么严格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有可以哭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 在厕所里哭的话就不会有人注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的时候就哭 有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在好好哭一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的时候却不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大后这种情况少不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要玩具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选一个吧 我给你买
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是买个适合女孩子的比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣也挺奇怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 玩你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:04:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为一个快乐的暑假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢 和我这样的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路黑小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫 难道不认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的比较晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脸上有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别这样盯着人家的脸看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么话想说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在害怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再大声吼了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我妈妈的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问早苗阿姨去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问她 她不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才来问我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问早苗阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说我不愿意和你说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把帽子戴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要走不少路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看得更清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把脚分开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真轻啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑太远哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是来对了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只是在这附近玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有跑多远的啊 真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候再给你买个一样的 好不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的话也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真固执呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到那边去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别走开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是冈崎朋也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问… 您认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是冈崎史乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你父亲 冈崎直幸的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一位叫古河的人联络我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是在这里就能等到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是早苗阿姨吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经长这么大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有和您见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你还很小的时候 在这里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在你母亲敦子过世之后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸还在赎罪中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该已经出狱回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段回忆想必非常痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子以前并不是这么蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时敦子和直幸都还是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然周围的人都反对他们结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过直幸依然从高中退学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一间狭小的公寓里开始了两人的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当时 真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着自己所爱的人而生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此 那孩子就已经很幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后 敦子的腹中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小小的祝福之中 你诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这份幸福没能持续多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦子因车祸而过世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那孩子来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无法再振作起来的变故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 还不能就此绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时还有年幼的你在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定要亲手把这个孩子抚养成人」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那一天 从这个地方开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸就紧牵着你的手 开始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后的日子是那孩子一生中最努力的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次被辞退 辗转奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也从未松开过你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用仅有的一点钱给你买玩具 让你吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你牺牲了自己所有的运气和成功的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管有时候对你会很严格 很粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一切都是为了能把你好好抚养成人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 对于直幸来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常辛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了排遣工作上的辛酸 他开始借酒消愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了之后对你动粗的事情也有过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 那孩子还是选择和你一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 当你到了能自己决定自己人生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸已经失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作 信赖 运气 朋友 所有一切都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你现在的情况和当时的直幸很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正因为如此 我才想把这番话告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能知道直幸是一个怎样的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常买零食给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牵着手去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 你认为直幸是个不称职的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是比他更不称职的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那一天的老爸处在相同的境况中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的我却那么软弱 那么没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么软弱 那么不中用 那么没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 依然为自己的孩子竭尽了所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为那孩子感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人 他也许有很多失败的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为父亲 他非常了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这下就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子实在是太过努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了该让他休息一下的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你转告直幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「快回来吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在这片土地上等着那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她叫汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再给你买个新的吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是独一无二的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店里不还有很多在卖的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为我选 为我买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来旅行 觉得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以陪在你身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前一直 很长一段时间都是个不称职的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从今以后会为了汐而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以陪在你身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天失去了一个很重要的东西 所以很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用忍着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能哭的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有爸爸的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想听妈妈的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就坐到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈啊 是个好像随时都会哭出来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到她的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那么没有自信 那么软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆站在学校的那条坡道下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你知道她在坡道下说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然闭着眼睛说「豆沙面包」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妈妈的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出自己想吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而来让自己鼓起勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨那个时候忙于工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没有给她做便当的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬去拜托的话 早苗阿姨肯定会挤出时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈并没有那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就是这样的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊 妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连你也哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因为回忆起了妈妈的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们继续说下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她那时想要演舞台剧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.03,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么叫演舞台剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能守护的 无可替代的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
